        <item>
            <title>PS5 Pro 终于正式亮相　三大效能提升 + 推出日期和价格</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/10/ps5-pro-announced/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=ps5-pro-announced</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/10/ps5-pro-announced/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[蓝骨]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 15:46:51 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏情报]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[PS5]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[PS5 Pro]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[SONY]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1262213</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Sony 早前发表只有 9 分钟的「特别技术展示」，期间算是正式公布了传闻已久的 PS5 Pro，一如预期采用与 PS5 类似的外形设计，此外在效能上有三个主要的提升范畴，提供更流畅细致的游玩体验。<br /><span id="more-1262213"></span></p><h2>三大效能提升范畴</h2><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/1696127-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262217" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/1696127-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/1696127.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>PS5 架构主管 Mark Cerny 表示，PS5 Pro 搭载了比 PS5 更强劲的 GPU、先进的光线追踪技术以及自主 AI 驱动的画面升级。其中 GPU 方面运算单元比目前 PS5 多 67%，记忆体速度也快了 28%，使游戏渲染速度整体提升 45%。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/ps5technicalpresenta-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262218" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/ps5technicalpresenta-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/ps5technicalpresenta-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>在光线追踪效能方面，PS5 Pro 借着更强劲的 CPU，据称开发者将能够把效能提升两到三倍。此外，PS5 Pro 还搭载了 Sony 新开发的 AI 驱动技术「PlayStation Spectral Super Resolution」（PSSR），类似于 Nvidia DLSS 或 AMD FSR 的画面升级技术，可以提升 PlayStation 游戏的帧率和画面品质。PSSR 升级技术将取代游戏原有的时间性抗锯齿或升采样实现方式，提升游戏体验。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/ps5protechnicalprese-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262219" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/ps5protechnicalprese-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/ps5protechnicalprese.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/ps5protechnicalprese-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262220" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/ps5protechnicalprese-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/ps5protechnicalprese-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>向下支援 PS4 游戏提升</h2><p>如果游戏不支援 PS5 Pro 的加强效能的话也没有意思，而 Sony 就因此加入了「游戏增强」选项，可以直接向下支援超过 8,500 款 PS4 游戏，提升效能和稳定性，部分 PS4 游戏更可以透过这个功能提升解像度。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/screenshot-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262215" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/screenshot-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/screenshot.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>PS5 Pro 将于 11 月 7 日上市，售价为 699.99 美元（约 HK$5,458）。Mark Cerny 透露，PS5 Pro 的一个主要目标是让玩家不必在性能和画质之间作出取舍，他解释「玩家约有四分之三的时间选择性能模式」，而在 PS5 Pro 上就可以两者兼得。PS5 Pro 将支援 Wi-Fi 7、VRR 和 8K 显示，值得一提的是，PS5 Pro 本身并不设光碟机，玩家需要另购光碟机来玩实体光碟游戏。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/458770744_9485412306-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262239" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/458770744_9485412306-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/458770744_9485412306.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/11/ps5-pro-enhanced/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">首批 PS5 Pro Enhanced 游戏揭晓　完整发挥新机效能</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/10/sony-technical-presentation-sep-10/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">PlayStation 今晚 11 点有发布会　市场揣测或公布 PS5 Pro</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/06/sony-ps-30th-seems-leak-ps5-pro/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Sony 官方隐约展示 PS5 Pro 设计　PlayStation 30 周年贺图藏玄机</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/10/ps5-pro-announced/game-channel/">PS5 Pro 终于正式亮相　三大效能提升 + 推出日期和价格</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
