        <item>
            <title>华为 Mate XT 三折机到货严禁拆封　售卖点如提前拆封罚款 50 万人民币</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/10/huawei-mate-xt-today-early-disclose-may-cause-penalty-of-500k/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=huawei-mate-xt-today-early-disclose-may-cause-penalty-of-500k</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/09/10/huawei-mate-xt-today-early-disclose-may-cause-penalty-of-500k/mobile-phone/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 12:00:36 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提电话]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Huawei]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Huawei Mate XT]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Mate XT]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[华为]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[华为 Mate XT]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[电话]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1262112</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>早前我们报道过，华为官方宣布三折手机 Mate XT 接受预订后，有二手平台在华为还未宣布官方定价之时就已表示会基于原价额外加 1.6 万元收购（<a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/08/huawei-mate-xt/mobile-phone/">相关报道</a>）。华为今日（9 月 10 日）召开发布会，正式推出三折叠手机 Mate XT 「非凡大师」。据悉消费者对 Mate XT 反应热烈，预订订单已突破 310 万部。</p><p>据中国媒体引述消息人士指，华为已经将部分 Mate XT 现货送达售卖门市，而华为对 Mate XT 的保密工作尤其严格，据中国媒体《新浪财经》报道，送达门市的新机外包装贴有警告封条，上面写明「发布会召开前，未经授权禁止开启，提前拆封罚款 50 万元（人民币，约港币 54.77 万元）起」。</p><p>Mate XT 非凡大师是华为首款采用了全新升级的折叠萤幕技术的三折叠手机，配备素皮背壳与高辨识度的八角形摄像模组。根据华为官方发布的宣传影片，这款手机在折叠后尺寸与主流大屏手机相当，而展开后则可转变为平板电脑。据悉华为 Mate XT 「非凡大师」有 256GB、512GB 和 1TB 三款容量可选，售价分别是 19,999、21,999 和 23,999 人民币（分别为约港币 21,908、24,093 及 26,283 元），主要针对高阶消费者，市场反应非常积极。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1262144" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/20240910180004-694x475.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="475" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/20240910180004-694x475.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/20240910180004.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲图片来源：<a href="https://portal.sina.com.hk/technology/sina/2024/09/10/965393/%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BAmate-xt%E5%94%AE%E5%83%B919999%E5%85%83%E8%B5%B7%EF%BC%8C%E9%A4%98%E6%89%BF%E6%9D%B1%EF%BC%9A%E7%94%A2%E5%93%81%E6%88%90%E6%9C%AC%E9%9D%9E%E5%B8%B8%E9%AB%98/">新浪香港</a></p><p>图片、资料来源：<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jnN9xqUJuTM&amp;t=1s&amp;ab_channel=SparrowsNews">Sparrow News@YouTube</a>、<a href="https://finance.sina.com.cn/roll/2024-09-10/doc-incnrwyp7925734.shtml">新浪财经</a>、<a href="https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%85%A9%E5%B2%B8/article/20240910/s00004/1725901276617/">明报</a>、<a href="https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2022522/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B-%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BAMate-XT-%E4%BB%8A%E8%88%89%E8%A1%8C%E7%99%BC%E4%BD%88%E6%9C%83%E9%A0%90%E8%A8%82%E5%B7%B2%E7%A0%B4310%E8%90%AC-%E9%96%80%E5%BA%97%E6%8F%90%E5%89%8D%E6%8B%86%E5%B0%81%E7%BD%B0%C2%A550%E8%90%AC%E8%B5%B7">星岛</a>、<a href="https://portal.sina.com.hk/technology/sina/2024/09/10/965393/%E8%8F%AF%E7%82%BAmate-xt%E5%94%AE%E5%83%B919999%E5%85%83%E8%B5%B7%EF%BC%8C%E9%A4%98%E6%89%BF%E6%9D%B1%EF%BC%9A%E7%94%A2%E5%93%81%E6%88%90%E6%9C%AC%E9%9D%9E%E5%B8%B8%E9%AB%98/">新浪香港</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/11/huawei-matebook-x-pro-review-2/review-2/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【评测】Huawei MateBook X Pro　外形　手感　屏幕　键盘　功能　效能开箱评测</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/09/huawei-mate-xt-2mill-order/fun-tech/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">华为三折手机 Mate XT 预购超 200 万部，二手平台加 1.6 万元收机</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/08/huawei-mate-xt/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">华为 Mate XT 非凡大师三折叠手机曝光，配备素皮背壳及八角形摄像头模组</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/09/10/huawei-mate-xt-today-early-disclose-may-cause-penalty-of-500k/mobile-phone/">华为 Mate XT 三折机到货严禁拆封　售卖点如提前拆封罚款 50 万人民币</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
